The '''blockade of Zolan''' occurred during the [[Imperial Era/Legends|Imperial Era]]. After the rise of the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]], the [[Imperial Military/Legends|Imperial Military]] [[Blockade/Legends|blockaded]] the planet [[Zolan/Legends|Zolan]], homeworld of the [[Zolander]]s and the [[Changeling/Legends|shape-shifting]] [[Clawdite/Legends|Clawdites]]. [[Imperial Intelligence/Legends|Imperial Intelligence]] sought to restrict travel to and from the planet in order to prevent any changelings from aiding rebels. The blockade began early on in the reign of the Galactic Empire and remained while the Empire was in power. Unfortunately, the death of [[Emperor/Legends|Emperor]] [[Palpatine/Legends|Palpatine]] that ended the blockade led to an era of tensions between the Zolander and the Clawdites, culminating in a full-scale [[Zolan Civil War|civil war]].<ref name="UoSGtILTC" />

